# Passwork Provider

The Passwork provider allows Terraform to manage resources in [Passwork](https://passwork.pro) — a self-hosted password manager for teams.

## Token refresh and session caching

Passwork API tokens are short-lived. On first use, supply `access_token` and `refresh_token`. The provider automatically refreshes tokens when they expire and caches the new pair in `.terraform/passwork_session` (AES-encrypted). Subsequent runs load the cached session, so you only need to visit the Passwork UI again when both tokens have expired (typically after months).

